title: Beats x Disclosure - Latch: Beat by Beat
description:
Disclosure deconstructs the recording of their groundbreaking hit "Latch", featuring vocalist Sam Smith and songwriter Jimmy Napes. 

Directed by David Black.
Cinematography by Drew Bienemann.
Edited by Jonathan Dortch.
Digital Technician Brendan Pattengale.
Produced by Native Pictures.
